@startuml repl_save
title REPL Save: Patch vs. Full-Save Fallback

participant "Software Architect" as architect
participant "Interactive" as bausteinsicht_cli_interactive
participant "Validate" as bausteinsicht_model_validate
participant "Patch" as bausteinsicht_model_patch
participant "Loader" as bausteinsicht_model_loader

architect -> bausteinsicht_cli_interactive : 1. add / remove / edit ... then `save`
bausteinsicht_cli_interactive -> bausteinsicht_model_validate : 2. Validate(in-memory model)
bausteinsicht_model_validate --> bausteinsicht_cli_interactive : 3. valid, or 'save aborted — N validation error(s)'
bausteinsicht_cli_interactive -> bausteinsicht_model_patch : 4. pure additions: PatchInsert / AppendArrayEntry (comments preserved)
bausteinsicht_cli_interactive -> bausteinsicht_model_loader : 5. any modification/deletion: Save(model.jsonc) full rewrite (comments may be lost)
bausteinsicht_cli_interactive --> architect : 6. 'Saved'

@enduml
